Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:03.98,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.42,0:00:14.03,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's Make a Game!" Pitch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.66,0:00:13.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I fell asleep...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:24.14,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, kouhai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.14,0:00:26.39,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you painting on my walls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:28.09,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Milky Way Cat, Nyapollon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:28.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Nyapollon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:31.31,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's a character from a \Nfull-length anime series that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:33.14,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been working on since \NI was in kindergarten!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.14,0:00:33.59,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.34,0:00:36.59,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,...is the robot protagonist, Nyapollon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:40.10,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,He's a weapon designed to protect Earth \Nfrom the Nyangoro space invaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:42.40,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,After they beat their\N first Nyangoro invader,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:44.45,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,they study it, cultivate its cells...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.45,0:00:49.06,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and warp space-time to \Ncreate a hybrid robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.06,0:00:52.83,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,However, it can only \Nbe piloted by someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.83,0:00:58.45,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,who has experienced the \Nworst life has to offer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.79,0:01:00.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What a ridiculous plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:02.69,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Nekoko, the heroine, \Nhas a boyfriend, Nekosuke,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.69,0:01:05.71,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,who gets killed by the enemy \Ncommander, Ein the Hunchback!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:07.79,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Nekoko decides to cast aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:10.06,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,her sadness and pilot Nyapollon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:12.81,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,But Ein the Hunchback is so powerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.81,0:01:14.50,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that 60% of the human race is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:16.13,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Um, how long does this story go on for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.50,0:01:16.13,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,already dead by the start of the series.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.48,0:01:17.70,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,52 episodes altogether!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:19.14,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I could probably summarize it in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:20.65,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,How about you stop now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:22.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I woke up early for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:24.21,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be late on the \Nfirst day of second semester...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.21,0:01:25.91,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,That clock's stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.91,0:01:26.64,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.01,0:01:30.31,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Because I removed the batteries!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.31,0:01:32.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do stupid pranks like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:35.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,And don't just carry on \Ndrawing in silence over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:09.83,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Suimei University of the \NArts Cultural Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:09.83,Eptitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,1)}#09 The Fall Storm is Here
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.09,0:03:09.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I just made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:13.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You should've said something \Nto me before you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:15.25,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'll start doing \Nthat as of tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:16.65,Saku-main,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:18.92,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama-san moved into Sakura Hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:21.13,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so she could be with Kanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.39,0:03:23.61,Saku-main,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Kanda basically ordered her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.61,0:03:25.18,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to go and move in with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:27.42,Saku-main,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that they share the same room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.42,0:03:28.88,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami's so forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:30.89,Saku-main,GIRL C,0000,0000,0000,,This is strictly confidential,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:32.82,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I heard that she's already pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:34.31,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not pregnant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:37.65,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? You're not \Ndenying the rest of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:39.78,Saku-main,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,You really did move into \NSakura Hall, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:41.48,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I did, but we have different rooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:43.69,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, don't just keep quiet! Tell them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:46.36,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I've been caught up in this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:46.36,Saku-overlap,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Save me, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:48.09,Saku-overlap,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You can do it, husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:48.72,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:54.51,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Quit bothering Nanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:54.51,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Miyahara?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:55.36,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Miyahara-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:59.72,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,I-I mean, quit bothering \NNanami and Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:02.12,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata's not an immoral guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:03.14,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:06.23,Saku-main,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,But they really do live \Nunder the same roof, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:09.29,Saku-main,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,Miyahara, why are you \Ngetting so huffy about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:12.33,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, because I... you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:14.59,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata's my friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:16.98,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can't just ignore any \Nweird rumors about him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.85,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,I shared a room with Sorata...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.85,0:04:20.97,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,in the regular dorms in our first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:22.39,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you're gonna share a roof...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:24.32,Saku-overlap,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why are you blushing, Miyahara?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:24.32,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,with someone if you live in dorms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:25.06,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:28.99,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it! You're the one \Ndating Kanda-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:30.20,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:30.20,Saku-overlap,GIRL C,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.91,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want Nanami to take \Nyour beloved Kanda-kun away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:34.75,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Miyahara-kun, how gallant!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:36.05,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I support your relationship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:36.05,Saku-overlap,GIRL A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:38.13,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun and Miyahara-kun are an item.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.42,Saku-main,GIRL B,0000,0000,0000,,They do make a good couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:41.73,Saku-main,GIRL C,0000,0000,0000,,So they're both gay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:43.86,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Miyahara...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:45.88,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,How did it come to this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:48.00,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kanda-kun! Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:49.16,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You can love whoever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:52.28,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever you choose to love, \Nwe'll still be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:53.18,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get carried away with the crowd!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:56.10,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,...which is how I had \Nsuch a terrible first day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:59.06,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,of second semester because of weird \Nrumors going around about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:01.34,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because of the way \Nthe residents of Sakura Hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:03.85,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,conduct themselves on a daily basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:06.41,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, let's follow the rules...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:08.33,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and lead pure and proper high school lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:09.53,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:10.83,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:11.79,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Only say it once!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:12.54,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Okaaaay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:13.43,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't draw it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.43,0:05:15.58,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you're here, Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.49,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.49,0:05:19.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I had terrible things \Nhappen to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:23.38,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, I almost got hit \Nby a hearse on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:25.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,When I tried to get out of the \Nway, I stepped in the gutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:28.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I even got clawed by a black \Ncat that just happened to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:30.93,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about an unlucky first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:34.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,All I can do is pray \Nnothing else bad happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:37.74,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't involve us in your misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.74,Saku-overlap,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun, settle down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:39.15,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:45.07,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,This weather really does seem foreboding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:47.29,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Must be a fall storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:05:55.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:56.83,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Only say it once!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:03.30,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening. I apologize \Nfor dropping in so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.46,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,A-A foreigner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:08.97,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you dazzled by my beauty?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:13.31,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You're dazzled by my \Nbeauty, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:17.58,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I-I cannot speak English.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:19.01,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's Rita.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:19.77,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:28.02,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be keeping \Nwell, Mashiro. I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.02,0:06:29.92,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:31.99,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,She's a real doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:34.56,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,She's a babe! Mashiro-chan, \Ndo you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:36.28,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Rita.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:38.29,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Good to see you \Nagain, Chihiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:40.33,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:43.58,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,She was Mashiro's roommate \Nwhen she lived in England.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:46.55,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Rita Ainsworth. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:49.51,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,But, Rita, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:52.83,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Cinderella's magic has been dispelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:54.23,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Or as you Japanese might say:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.23,0:06:56.47,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to take Kaguyahime \Nback to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:01.98,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro, please come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:04.46,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to England with me immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:05.80,Saku-main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:10.15,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You came here to take\N Mashiro-chan back with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:15.29,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I cannot allow Mashiro to \Ncontinue studying manga here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:17.91,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:21.26,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:23.38,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,But please reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:28.17,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you realize how much \Npotential you have in those fingers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:33.08,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Your paintings may even \Ngo down in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:38.28,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of people itching\N to see your next masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.86,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you scratch that itch?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:44.62,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You encouraged me to draw manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:48.04,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I only taught you how \Nto use a computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:49.80,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I never encouraged you to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:50.69,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Rita...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:55.33,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sit back and watch you waste \Nyour time and talent any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:57.15,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Mashiro. Together, we—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.15,0:07:58.30,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:02.37,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, just listen to me, Mashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:04.71,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:08.95,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you sure about this, Shiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.95,0:08:11.47,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro, I won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:14.39,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I will take you back to England with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:15.79,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:22.28,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're going after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:24.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just leave her out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:26.68,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You want Mashiro-chan to \Ngo back to England?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:30.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just leave her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:36.82,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you'd come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:39.59,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You knew I would come?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:41.87,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,When a damsel's in distress,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:46.43,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,a kind boy always comes to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:54.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I brought her back here, \Nbut this is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:58.11,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She immediately said she \Nwanted to take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:09:00.25,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, English people...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:02.15,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:05.94,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why aren't you wearing any clothes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:07.61,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a change of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:10.27,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I intended to return home straight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.94,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Just put some clothes on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:15.45,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,This belongs to Mashiro, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:17.45,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I do her laundry for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:19.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,As her former roommate, \Nyou must understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:23.12,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You're on Mashiro Duty in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:25.57,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You did that in England, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:28.94,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Over there, I was on Mashiro Duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:31.31,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You can look this way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:35.34,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro drew half of this, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:36.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell just by looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:41.36,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I've been with Mashiro since we met...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:43.14,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,at my grandfather's studio when \Nwe were six years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:47.31,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't draw anymore, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:49.88,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:52.65,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You'll let me stay in this \Nroom tonight, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:54.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're staying here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.49,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't booked a hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:10:01.31,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you the type of person who throws \Nsomeone out after you've taken them in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:04.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I'll sleep in the dining room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:07.12,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,No, you'll sleep here, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,With you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:11.84,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to tell me about \NMashiro's life in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.28,0:10:14.76,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to know \Nwhat Mashiro's life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:16.68,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,was like in England?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:22.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Is Shiina really that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:24.25,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro's overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:25.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Overwhelming?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:28.29,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me wish she'd just disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:31.11,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You should be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:35.23,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay by Mashiro's side, \Nyou'll be destroyed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:37.03,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Just like I have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:39.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:52.01,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Her paintings will go \Ndown in history...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:55.14,Saku-thought,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Please reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:59.88,Saku-thought,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you realize how much \Npotential you have in those fingers?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:21.16,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, it's already past eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:23.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! Don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.06,0:11:26.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Our relationship is pure, proper, \Nand appropriate for high schoolers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:27.92,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine that you let her stay here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.92,0:11:29.91,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,but you've become awfully \Nclose, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:31.50,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, are you on Rita's side?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:32.66,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:33.44,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:37.56,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I have decided to stay in Sorata's room...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:39.88,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,until you agree to come \Nback to England with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:41.45,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Without even consulting me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:42.26,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata's my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:43.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:44.84,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, kouhai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:46.32,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You have now reached adulthood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:48.96,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the day I relinquish \Nmy title of Flying Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:50.22,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,It's all up to you now, Sorata!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.22,0:11:53.44,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda, I've always thought \Nyou were pretty annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:57.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That has no bearing \Non this situation at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:58.94,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,You're too loud first thing in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:00.82,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place, a zoo \Nduring breeding season?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.68,0:12:04.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.69,0:12:06.78,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:07.87,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:10.29,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You! You came out of your room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.50,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen some \Nof your faces before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.28,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:19.91,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Akasaka Ryunosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:22.20,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the occupant of Room 102.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:32.71,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,You have received a message!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:41.68,Saku-main,KOHARU,0000,0000,0000,,Akasaka-kun, are my\N lessons boring you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:45.36,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in most \Nthings in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.83,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,And I hate women, \Nso don't talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:51.07,Saku-main,KOHARU,0000,0000,0000,,You finally came to school for \Nthe first time in five months.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:55.13,Saku-main,KOHARU,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if you at least stopped eating \Ntomatoes and listened to my lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:58.23,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Tomatoes are nutritious and scrumptious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:13:01.67,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only here to increase \Nmy attendance scores,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:03.09,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so there's no reason for me to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:06.02,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,If you have a problem with \Nthat, you should come up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:08.55,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,with a lesson I can actually take \Nsome interest in, Shiroyama Koharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:11.16,Saku-main,KOHARU,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you talk \Nbalk to your teacher?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:12.06,Saku-main,KOHARU,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:14.57,Saku-main,KOHARU,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to tell \NChihiro-chan about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:15.85,Sign,NOTE,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do about Rita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:21.78,Sign,NOTE,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want Mashiro to go back to England?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:27.50,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Some things can't be done over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:35.98,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No good will come of me overthinking this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:38.54,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina's the one who has to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:42.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Here, your laundry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:43.38,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:50.26,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:52.81,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate Melon Bun
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:54.52,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're a Sorata idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:55.89,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of idiot is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:59.78,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Let the "Japanese and English \NDeclaration of Friendship...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:01.82,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lines I Always Wanted to \NSay Once" event begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:02.86,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:02.86,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:05.61,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you half of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:06.96,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:09.39,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Driver, follow that car!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:11.97,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Rittan! You're next!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:13.34,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:17.24,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want the good news \Nor the bad news first?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.24,0:14:18.15,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're next!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:19.67,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm next? U-Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:22.29,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't spout such nonsense... or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:23.98,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:25.76,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Will you go on just one date with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:28.38,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, I'd like to go out tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:28.99,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:30.31,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.31,0:14:34.11,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I'm busy \Nfor the next ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:34.81,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.16,0:14:37.29,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind waiting ten years...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:39.13,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to go on a date with \Nsuch an incredible girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:39.77,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:42.05,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.05,0:14:43.10,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,He made that all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:44.66,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,They're all lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:45.52,Saku-overlap,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,We're speaking out of order.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:46.82,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,We skipped Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:49.73,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro-chan, it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:52.34,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata is an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:59.58,Saku-main,GIRL A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you come up with something\N for this year's culture festival yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:02.36,Saku-main,GIRL B,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I should do an oil painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:03.82,Saku-main,GIRL B,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's go buy some paints together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:04.95,Saku-main,GIRL A,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:06.51,Saku-main,GIRL B,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Shiho.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:08.45,Saku-main,GIRL B,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come with us, Shiho?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:09.49,Saku-main,GIRL A,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:10.87,Saku-main,SHIHO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:22.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina, I'm here to—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:39.00,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I have to tell you \Nthis now, so I'm texting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:42.07,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm confused, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.99,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She just suddenly turned up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:46.04,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,and said she was taking \Nyou back to England.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:49.30,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,When she said your paintings \Nwould go down in history,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:51.10,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,it really made me think.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:55.52,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It made me wonder what's \Nactually best for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.69,0:15:58.87,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not on Rita's side,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:02.94,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not sure I'm \Non your side, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:05.01,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:10.90,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really looking forward to \Nyour serialized manga. I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:12.86,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Sending
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:18.50,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Does she even know how \Nto check her messages?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.23,0:16:22.00,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Received Message\N{\b1}Shiina Mashiro{\b0}\NRe: No Subject
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:29.94,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Received Message\N{\b1}Shiina Mashiro{\b0}\NRe: No Subject\NYou
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.18,0:16:32.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:34.30,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,For "Sorata is an idiot."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:36.35,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't have "you" in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:42.10,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Men, the day has finally arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:41.37,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hey! Misaki-senpai, I \Ncan see your underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:43.00,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Come down from there, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:45.24,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we've assembled the \Nstrongest warriors of Sakura Hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.24,0:16:47.43,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we must harness our power of friendship...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:50.14,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and take control of the culture festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:51.90,Saku-overlap,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, she's saying \Nthat the residents of Sakura Hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:54.81,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,should band together and do \Nsomething for the culture festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:55.84,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:57.34,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:58.40,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:00.91,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Well, I'm all for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:03.47,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Ryunosuke says: "No problems here."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.47,0:17:06.01,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone approves, so it's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.01,0:17:07.19,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,If we're gonna do something,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:09.27,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we should make something \Nonly Sakura Hall could make!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:10.38,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:13.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai and Shiina\N could do the art,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:16.02,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-san could write the script, \Nand Aoyama could provide the voices...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:19.89,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,With talent like that, we could \Nmake an amazing video.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:23.09,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,And Sakura Hall even has the Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:24.85,Sign,NOTE,0000,0000,0000,,Ryunosuke
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:24.24,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,A programmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.24,0:17:24.85,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,The Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:26.33,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She means Akasaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:28.24,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,His name's Ryunosuke, \N and the "ryu" means "dragon."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:32.78,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}{\b1}Mitaka Jin{\b0}: Misaki and Mashiro will do the artwork, I'll \Nwrite the script, and Aoyama-san will do the voices.\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: Same as always.\N{\b1}Mitaka Jin{\b0}: Could you use your talents to help us make something \Ninteractive like a game instead of just a simple animation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:31.94,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Should we create something that \Nuses a controller, like a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:32.78,Saku-main,RYUNOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:36.66,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But if we do that, only one \Nperson at a time can enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:40.75,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that we can make it an attraction \Neveryone can participate in?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:41.83,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:44.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,For example, when the audience claps,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:46.46,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the character moves, \Nor raises its arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:49.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I was just wondering if there was \Na way to make something...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:51.89,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that allows everyone to work \Ntogether to move the story forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:58.27,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, kouhai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:17:59.67,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I think that sounds fun, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.67,0:18:01.10,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's a great idea, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:03.38,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good! I knew you \Ncould do it, kouhai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:05.28,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I can feel your burning passion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:05.28,Saku-overlap,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'll notify Ryunosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:06.09,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,If you've made a decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:08.96,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,be sure to submit your plan to the \NStudent Council as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:10.90,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You can't participate if you \Ndon't receive permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:13.67,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,The Student Council...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:14.84,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:17.05,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing. In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:18.61,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we'd better start developing\N our content soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:21.90,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,We're starting from scratch so \Nwe don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:24.46,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Nyapollon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:27.27,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, Mashiron!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:30.13,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Ryunosuke says that if \Nwe borrow equipment...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:32.50,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,from a hardware store, we can \Nturn Sorata's idea into reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:35.41,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing! Just what \Nis Akasaka-kun, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:35.41,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:37.65,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,The director will be... Kouhai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:39.05,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:39.68,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:40.72,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,No objections!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:41.93,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you, Kanda-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:43.14,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Mitaka Jin{\b0}: Sorata will be the director.\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: No complaints here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:44.97,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:50.03,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? I'm supposed to... lead this bunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:02.81,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,A culture festival? That sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:05.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but the situation has \Ngotten a little out of hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:06.62,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Rita.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:08.50,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Mashiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:11.33,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Rita, sleep in my room from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:13.42,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,What brought about this change of heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:15.67,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You can't sleep in \NSorata's room anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:17.98,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.98,0:19:20.79,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike Jin, Sorata's good for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:23.47,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Do you have any idea how hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:25.19,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,my rationality's been fighting every night?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:27.22,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind sleeping in Mashiro's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:28.21,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:30.29,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,But I have one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:31.12,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:32.23,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.98,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,This Sunday, go on a date with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:35.69,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:41.36,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:43.49,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,...where we're going on our date.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:45.29,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:46.31,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:47.92,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't embarrass me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:50.23,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,by turning me down in front \Nof a hotel, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:51.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No, let's wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:52.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We should definitely wait on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:53.65,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:55.30,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:57.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What are you going to do to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:00.17,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:06.97,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:10.00,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:12.15,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to believe in \Na coincidence like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.15,0:20:13.22,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.22,0:20:17.36,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're all here, the four\N of us should go in together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:18.36,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The four of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:22.36,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,European Young Artists \NModern Art Exhibit
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.60,0:20:22.36,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,So, this was your actual destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:26.08,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm kinda nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:27.92,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:31.71,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:43.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:48.45,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to show you this painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.51,0:21:09.83,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,It's the last painting Mashiro \Ndid before she came to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.74,0:21:21.31,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Has this helped you understand\N Mashiro a little better?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.48,0:21:34.04,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I read the manga Mashiro \Nwrote over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.03,0:21:37.27,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get manga,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.11,0:21:43.86,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but even so, I didn't think it was \Nworth giving up painting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.35,0:21:50.33,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Sorata?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:21:57.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina should...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:06.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,return to the world of fine arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.72,0:23:35.84,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,My routine has been upended \Nby that freeloader.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.87,0:23:40.98,NextEptitle,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(270,1)}#10 Hate Hate, Love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.84,0:23:39.18,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Why's she going to the bathroom \Nat 6:45 in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.18,0:23:40.98,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,That's the time I use it!
